info.senderName: NWS Duluth (Northeast Minnesota and Northern Wisconsin)
info.headline: Dense Fog Advisory issued June 15 at 9:19PM CDT until June 16 at 7:00AM CDT by NWS Duluth
info.description: ...DENSE FOG ADVISORY REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL 7 AM CDT THURSDAY... * WHAT...Visibility 1/4 to 1 mile in dense fog. * WHERE...Southern Cook County. This includes the Tribal Lands of the Grand Portage Reservation. * WHEN...Until 7 AM CDT Thursday. * IMPACTS...Hazardous driving conditions due to low visibility. * ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Fog make drift in and out off Lake Superior this evening. Fog will be the most dense right along the coast of Lake Superior and on Highway 61.
info.instruction: If driving, slow down, use your headlights, and leave plenty of distance ahead of you.
